<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1 class="about-heading">About Me and Neutrino Software Company</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "CurtisDunnePic.jpg", width: 250, alt: "Neutrino Logo", class: 'profile-image' %>

        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                >
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>With over two decades of designing, planning, creating, and distributing <bold>custom software solutions</bold>, I
          have both a wide and deep skill-set in numerous mobile and web technologies.  What this means to you is that I can design and
          create a custom software solution for your small or medium sized business.
        </p>

        <p>Whether it be an <strong>iOS app</strong>, a <strong>Web App</strong>, <em>and/or</em> just about anything else
          in between, I can get it done for you <strong>on time</strong>, and <strong>at an affordable price</strong>.  Check out my Portfolio page to
          get an idea of what I am capable of doing for you.
        </p>

        <p><strong><em>Neutrino Software Company</em></strong> is my latest focus and passion. After over 15 years as CEO of <strong><em>Acme Software Company</em></strong> (and then
          <strong><em>Acme Computer Services</em></strong>), I am going back to my roots by helping out small & mid-sized businesses achieve their dreams
          and improve their bottom line via automation, mobile, and web technologies.
        </p>

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History

          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="jobHistory"
          >
            Education

          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card about-history-card">
              CafeX, New York, NY. | Wales, Great Britain
              <hr>
              Redlist, Salt Lake City, UT.
              <hr>
              Votec, San Diego, CA.
              <hr>
              ILTS, Vista, CA.
              <hr>
              School House Software, San Francisco, CA.
              <hr>
              Acme Computer Services, Peoria, IL. | Fallbrook, CA.
              <hr>
              Acme Software Company, Peoria, IL.
              <hr>
              Fidlar & Chambers, Morton, IL.
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card about-history-card">
              National University, LaJolla, CA.
              Bachelor of Science | Computer Science
              <hr>
              Illinois Central College, East Peoria, IL
              Associate of Science | Computer Science
              <hr>
              Illinois Central College | East Peoria, IL
              Associate of the Arts | Music Theory
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
